# Server-side
<reply>
<data nocheck="yes">
HTTP/1.1 416 Requested Range Not Satisfiable
Date: Thu, 09 Sep 2010 14:49:00 GMT
Accept-Ranges: bytes
Content-Length: 115

This is a long error message that is large enough that the test server is
guaranteed to split it into two packets.
</data>

<data1>
