# Client-side
<client>
<server>
http
</server>
 <name>
HTTP with invalid range then another URL
 </name>
 <command>
-r 10-22 http://%HOSTIP:%HTTPPORT/want/1117 http://%HOSTIP:%HTTPPORT/wantmore/11170001
</command>
</client>

